{"tid":2037282,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A]菇菇栽培研究室DELUXE極  有冇手足一齊種菇菇？","createTime":"2020-05-27T01:47:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T03:06:39.000Z","uid":33154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"938f65339f86e9f943174568c43dbab13225102c","tid":2037282,"uid":33154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T01:47:29.000Z","msg":"本作為栽培遊戲《菇菇栽培研究室》系列作品的「極限版」，為2012年所推出《觸摸偵探 菇菇栽培研究室 Deluxe》的續作版本。遊戲除了將收錄最多種類數量的菇菇，並以高畫質呈現外，也將追加3個新原木和稀有菇菇，可收穫的菇菇種類超過700種！讓玩家在回味舊作的同時也能體驗全新的內容，以及更便利的遊戲功能，享受遊戲樂趣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uc0B9Xt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuc0B9Xt.png&h=1aad94a2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qcULiQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqcULiQQ.png&h=45a77786&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UAvVF4d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUAvVF4d.png&h=04342a13&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MmWJPXB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMmWJPXB.png&h=f09dd312&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YWHdsKj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYWHdsKj.png&h=037782b4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wbXXUpD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwbXXUpD.png&h=336d980b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"21c5a64d54477e10a0410ff43767a7f0b300c1ab","tid":2037282,"uid":10790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T06:38:41.000Z","msg":"推推先"},{"pid":"9db2974e89634d62f02c3c761bb65739980ac0df","tid":2037282,"uid":89722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T07:12:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c041a91b601423a563d6196e91c24de7afd40ad5","tid":2037282,"uid":8570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T15:15:18.000Z","msg":"童年回憶<img src=\"/